30 TNode<String> CallJSArrayArrayJoinConcatToSequentialString(
31 TNode<FixedArray> fixed_array, TNode<IntPtrT> length, TNode<String> sep,
32 TNode<String> dest) {
33 TNode<ExternalReference> func = ExternalConstant(
34 ExternalReference::jsarray_array_join_concat_to_sequential_string());
35 TNode<ExternalReference> isolate_ptr =
36 ExternalConstant(ExternalReference::isolate_address(isolate()));
37 return UncheckedCast<String>(
38 CallCFunction(func,
39 MachineType::AnyTagged(), // <return> String
40 std::make_pair(MachineType::Pointer(), isolate_ptr),
41 std::make_pair(MachineType::AnyTagged(), fixed_array),
42 std::make_pair(MachineType::IntPtr(), length),
43 std::make_pair(MachineType::AnyTagged(), sep),
44 std::make_pair(MachineType::AnyTagged(), dest)));
45 }
46
47 protected:
